steps.html_instructions: Head southeast on 6th Ave N toward Charlotte Ave
Merge onto I-40 E/I-65 S via the ramp on the left to Knoxville/Huntsville

Keep right at the fork to continue on I-65 S, follow signs for Huntsville
Entering Alabama

Turn right onto AL-53 S/AL-6 E/US-231 S/US-82 E
Continue to follow AL-53 S/US-231 S

Turn right onto US-231 S/S Oates St
Continue to follow US-231 S
Entering Florida

Take the 3rd right onto FL-276 W/Penn Ave/Pennsylvania Ave
Continue to follow FL-276 W
Turn left onto the Interstate 10 E ramp to Tallahassee

Turn right onto US-27 S/N Monroe St (signs for Tallahassee)
Destination will be on the right
